Barakat Oyinlomo Quadre (amụrụ n'ụbọchị mbụ n'ọnwa Mee n'afọ 2003) bụ onye Naijiria na-egwu tenis. Ọ bụ onye Naijiria kachasị elu ugbu a na WTA ụmụ nwanyị otu
As of March 2018[update], ọ bụ onye mbụ na Naijiria, nke 9 na Africa na 945 n'ụwa na ụmụ nwanyị na-alụbeghị di.
Quadre nọchitere anya Naijiria na Billie Jean King Cup, na-eme nke mbụ ya na 2021.
Quadre malite ịgba tenis mgbe ọ dị afọ 4

Dị ka onye na-eto eto, ọ nọ n'ọkwa 173 na 17 Juunu 2019. Na 2015 ITF / CAT Junior Championship na Morocco, Quadre guzobere onwe ya dị ka otu n'ime ndị egwuregwu tennis kachasị mma n'Africa, ma nweta agụmakwụkwọ na High Performance Center na Morocco. Na 2016 ITF U-18 Championship, Quadre mere nkeji iri na ise nke ikpeazụ

N'afọ 2017, meriri Chakira Dermane nke Togo 6-0, 6-0 iji setịpụ esemokwu ikpeazụ na Sophia Biolay nke France. Na mba, a họpụtara ya ka ọ nọchite anya Naijiria na 2016 Africa Junior Tennis Championship. O meriri ITF / CAT U-16 Championship na Togo.
Na 2018 Lagos Open, Quadre meriri Airhunmwunde, 6-1, 6-0 iji ruo eru maka agba nke abụọ
N'egwuregwu ya ọzọ, Anna Sisková meriri ya wee pụọ n' asọmpi ahụ.
